name: ReviveConference
0:
”Alexa, open revive conference”
”when is the revive conference”
”who is speaking at the revive conference”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: revive conference
des: The Citrus Valley Association of Realtors becomes the first real estate organization to develop an Amazon Alexa skill for their 2018 Real Estate Revive Conference. Ask Revive Conference who are the speakers, who are the sponsors and tell me about Revive Conference. This special program has Amazon Alexa as the Co-host who is introducing the speakers, making announcements, and thanking the sponsors for their participation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
